# SpatialGenEval Notice

This directory contains code adapters for the SpatialGenEval benchmark.

## Attribution
- Paper: "Everything in Its Place: Benchmarking Spatial Intelligence of Text-to-Image Models" (arXiv:2601.20354).
- Source: AMAP-ML/SpatialGenEval (GitHub).

## Licensing
- The code in this directory is a clean-room implementation of the adapter and does not include any upstream code or datasets.
- Users are responsible for obtaining the benchmark data and ensuring compliance with its license.
